				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">SoE was mincing words. Yes, the minimum delay is 10 . . .
<br />

<br />
HOWEVER, haste technically, and this is where the mincing is, makes YOU faster, not the weapon.  So, EFFECTIVE delay can do less than 10. You can swing faster than once a second. 
<br />

<br />
See the play there: They can honestly say delay doesn't go below 10, but they say it meaning there aren't weapons with a delay below 10, since haste doesn't physically change the delay of the weapon.<br />_________________<br />Baron Aquendar Lerilon
<br />
56 Season Outrider of Tunare, The Tribunal
<br />
